{"tid":2216792,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"我好唔好彩返工撞到ex.","createTime":"2020-09-25T03:29:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T05:21:42.000Z","uid":71166,"like":3,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"541f7e94e5df5e8cd419cc3cccf5b153d545ba66","tid":2216792,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T03:29:43.000Z","msg":"ex.做影印機後援 做咗好多年<br />\n今日我call師傅整機<br />\n間公司話唔肯叫師傅嚟<br />\n話換粉盒要自己換<br />\n我咪彈佢話同事唔識你哋嚟教佢一次<br />\n仲話唔肯喎 我咪燥囉<br />\n間公司先話安排後援嚟 <br />\n<br />\n之後有個人打嚟確認<br />\n我心諗把聲咁熟<br />\n之後個後援一嚟我嘩咗聲<br />\n原來係ex. 我一下就留難佢<br />\n同個同事話我跟 問佢做咗防疫未<br />\n要佢落地下再做多次<br />\n再唔畀佢入去影印房 話入面其他機印緊嘢<br />\n要佢企咗廿分鐘，我先call我同事睇佢換粉<br />\n中段我再入去彈下佢公司服務<br />\n最後仲同我講呢啲好簡單 <br />\n下次公司唔會派人上嚟<br />\n之後話會send份問卷畀我喎<br />\n我同佢講一定寫得你「好好！」<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6Nod2YK.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6Nod2YK.gif&h=54d8cad9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"540641c237ebffda84a152d991e5f503c97cfebd","tid":2216792,"uid":155354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T03:31:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a65236d070ad9e48e81da1a9bff191de538b2bb3","tid":2216792,"uid":71166,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"540641c237ebffda84a152d991e5f503c97cfebd","tid":2216792,"uid":155354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T03:31:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T03:32:01.000Z","msg":"嗰時令我傷心嗱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i